cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with information theory and wireless sensor networks, which are both covered by cs.IT and cs.NI. The paper also discusses the behavior of the network under different conditions, which falls under the scope of cs.SY. The use of Gaussian fields and large deviations theory suggests a connection to cs.MA, while the investigation of energy efficiency and per-node information relates to cs.MM.
